.SS "const keyCode_Alt = 58"

.PP
platform-specific keycode for the Alt/Option key (generic, may not distinguish left/right) This constant contains the keycode value for detecting either Alt (Windows/Linux) or Option (Mac) key on the current platform\&. On Windows, this is the generic VK_MENU code that doesn't distinguish between left and right\&. On other platforms, it equals \fBkeyCode_LeftAlt\fP\&.

.PP
Platform values:**
.IP "\(bu" 2
Mac OS X: 58 (same as keyCode_LeftAlt)
.IP "\(bu" 2
Windows: 18 (0x12 - VK_MENU, generic alt key)
.IP "\(bu" 2
Linux/GLFW: 342 (same as keyCode_LeftAlt)
.PP

.PP
\fBSee also\fP
.RS 4
\fBkeyCode_LeftAlt\fP 

.PP
\fBkeyCode_RightAlt\fP 

.PP
\fBKeyEvent\fP 

.PP
\fBeventType_KeyDown\fP 

.PP
\fBeventType_KeyUp\fP 
.RE
.PP

