.SS "const keyCode_LeftAlt = 58"

.PP
platform-specific keycode for the left Alt/Option key This constant contains the correct keycode value for the left Alt (Windows/Linux) or Option (Mac) key on the current platform\&. Use this when checking #KeyEvent\&.keyCode in \fBeventType_KeyDown\fP or \fBeventType_KeyUp\fP event handlers to detect left Alt/Option key presses in a cross-platform way\&.

.PP
Platform values:**
.IP "\(bu" 2
Mac OS X: 58 (0x3A - NSEvent hardware keycode for left Option)
.IP "\(bu" 2
Windows: 164 (0xA4 - VK_LMENU virtual keycode for left Alt)
.IP "\(bu" 2
Linux/GLFW: 342 (GLFW_KEY_LEFT_ALT)
.PP

